<messaging:emailTemplate subject="{!RelatedTo.ASI_TnE_Sys_Resubmit__c}T&E Claim for {!If(ISNULL(RelatedTo.ASI_TnE_Payee_Employee__c), RelatedTo.Owner.Name, RelatedTo.ASI_TnE_Payee_Employee__r.Name)} is pending for your approval (#{!RelatedTo.Name})" recipientType="User" relatedToType="ASI_TnE_ClaimHeader__c">    <messaging:htmlEmailBody >        <html>            <body>                <p>Please note the following Travel &amp; Expense document is waiting for your approval/action. Kindly refer attached PDF report for more details.<br/>                請注意下列差旅費申請文件正待您簽核. 詳細資料請參閱附件PDF報表</p>                <table>                    <tr>                        <td>Owner Name 擁有者姓名</td>                        <td>: &nbsp; {!RelatedTo.Owner.Name}</td>                    </tr>                    <tr>                        <td>Employee Name 員工姓名</td>                        <td>: &nbsp; {!If(ISNULL(RelatedTo.ASI_TnE_Payee_Employee__c), RelatedTo.Owner.Name, RelatedTo.ASI_TnE_Payee_Employee__r.Name)}</td>                    </tr>                    <tr>                        <td>Claim Number 申請單號</td>                        <td>: &nbsp; {!RelatedTo.Name}</td>                    </tr>                    <tr>                        <td>Claim Amount 申請金額</td>                        <td>: &nbsp; <apex:outputText value="{0, number, ###,###,###,###}">                                <apex:param value="{!RelatedTo.ASI_TnE_TW_Total_Amount__c}" />                            </apex:outputText> ({!RelatedTo.ASI_TnE_Currency__c})                        </td>                    </tr>                    <tr>                        <td>Business Unit 事務單位</td>                        <td>: &nbsp; {!RelatedTo.ASI_TnE_Company__c}                        </td>                    </tr>                    <tr>                        <td>Department 部門</td>                        <td>: &nbsp; {!RelatedTo.ASI_TnE_Department_Division__c}                        </td>                    </tr>                    <tr>                        <td>Type of Expense Claim 費用申請型態</td>                        <td>: &nbsp; {!RelatedTo.ASI_TnE_Type__c}                        </td>                    </tr>                    <tr>                        <td>Remarks 備註</td>                        <td>: &nbsp; {!RelatedTo.ASI_TnE_Remarks__c}                        </td>                    </tr>                </table><p>To approve the Travel &amp; Expense document, click this&nbsp;<apex:outputLink value="{!LEFT($Api.Partner_Server_URL_140, FIND('.com/',$Api.Partner_Server_URL_140)+3)}/{!RelatedTo.id}">link</apex:outputLink> or by reply this email with keywords - APPROVE, YES, REJECT, NO<br/>                核准差旅費申請單. 回覆此信件請按此&nbsp;<apex:outputLink value="{!LEFT($Api.Partner_Server_URL_140, FIND('.com/',$Api.Partner_Server_URL_140)+3)}/{!RelatedTo.id}">連結</apex:outputLink> 或 輸入關鍵字- APPROVE, YES, REJECT, NO</p>            </body>        </html>    </messaging:htmlEmailBody>    <messaging:attachment renderAs="PDF"  filename="{!RelatedTo.name}"><c:ASI_TnE_ExpenseRptComponent headerId="{!RelatedTo.Id}" /></messaging:attachment></messaging:emailTemplate>